title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - Aircraft & Avionics Update 2 - first beta available
description:
In this video we will go through the changes in the first beta build of Aircraft & Avionics Update (AAU) 2 which has been released a few days ago. The initial build contains several fixes for issues reported by simmers. The focus is on improving both Boeings and you will see that a lot has been fixed/updated for both aircrafts.
